SUMMARY:Vintage Baseball at Story Inn
DESCRIPTION:Vintage Baseball is scheduled to return May 16.  Bring the family and enjoy America’s Favorite Past Time at Indiana’s oldest bed & breakfast!\nAn afternoon of Vintage Baseball!\nThree 5-inning games with 1864, 1869, and 1886 rules\nAdmission is free!\nFood and concessions available for purchase.\nGames start at 1pm, 2pm, and 3pm ending around 4:30pm.\n
