SUMMARY:ChamberFest Brown County – Verona Quartet Concert
DESCRIPTION:The Verona Quartet will perform a special concert at the Nashville United Methodist Church on Friday, April 24th, at 7:00pm. The string quartet is the Quartet-in-Resident at Oberlin College and Conservatory. They have performed as part of the annual ChamberFest Brown County concert festival in August, 2023. For the April 24th concert, they will perform works by Scarlatti, Glass, Janáček, and Beethoven. Admission is free and everyone is welcome to come and enjoy these world-class musicians.\n
