TRANSP:OPAQUE
SUMMARY:An Evening with Fred Minnick
DESCRIPTION:\n\n\nSome nights are easy to come by. Others—you feel them before they even begin. This is one of those nights. \n\n\n \n\n\nJoin us at Hard Truth Distilling Co. for an evening with Fred Minnick—a voice that’s helped shape how America understands whiskey, one honest story at a time. As part of his national tour for Bottom Shelf: How a Forgotten Brand of Bourbon Saved One Man’s Life, Fred brings his story to a place that lives and breathes the craft every day. \n\n\n \n\n\nThis won’t feel like a talk—it’ll feel like pulling up a chair and settling in. Over chef-curated appetizers and thoughtfully crafted cocktails, Fred will share stories from Bottom Shelf, including a live reading, along with reflections on bourbon’s deeper roots—where it comes from, and why it still matters. \n\n\n \n\n\nThere’s a weight to Fred’s words. Not because they’re loud—but because they’re true. And on this night, that truth meets the spirit of Hard Truth—where whiskey, story, and community come together in a way you don’t often find. \n\n\n \n\n\nThe evening closes with a book signing and a chance to meet Fred—so you don’t just hear the story, you carry it with you. \n\n\n \n\n\nWhat’s Included \n\n\n\nA copy of Bottom Shelf by Fred Minnick \nChef-curated appetizers \nSpecialty-developed cocktails (or alcohol-free pairings) \nA live reading and intimate conversation with Fred Minnick \nBook signing and meet-and-greet \n\n\n\n \n\n\nTicket Options \n\n\n\n\n\n$90 – Full experience with cocktails \n\n\n\n\n$65 – Alcohol-free experience \n\n\n\n \n\n\nIf you know bourbon, you know Fred. If you don’t—this is where the story starts. \n\n\n \n\n\nSeats are limited. Come early. Stay late. Discover the Truth. \n\n\n\nGet Your Tickets! ( https://mizunaracaskandstill.tripleseattickets.com/ )\n
URL:https://browncounty.com/events/an-evening-with-fred-minnick/
ORGANIZER;CN=Hard Truth Distilling Co.:MAILTO:events@bwqoht.com
CATEGORIES:Food &amp; Drink,Happening,Special Events
LOCATION:418 Old State Rd 46, Nashville, IN 47448
