SUMMARY:A Taste of Art — 10th year!
DESCRIPTION:This fun fundraiser hosted by the Rotary Club of Brown County promises to provide anticipation and excitement as attendees bid for contemporary and heritage art by local and area Indiana artists in the live and silent auctions.  Alcoholic beverage tastings (beer, wine, spirits) provided by local establishments are offered along with heavy hors d’oeuvres. Attendees can enjoy the tastings and bid on Silent Auction items beginning at 5:00pm and then participate in the spirited Live Auction beginning at 7:00.  All proceeds support the club’s focus on youth development activities and other community and international projects.\n \n
URL:https://browncounty.com/events/a-taste-of-art-10th-year/
