DESCRIPTION:Come discover all that camp has to offer! Our Open House is the perfect chance for families to explore our grounds, meet the staff, and get a feel for the camp experience. Tour cabins and program areas, ask questions about activities and schedules, and enjoy a taste of the community spirit that makes camp special. Whether you’re a first-time camper or a returning family, the Open House is a fun and relaxed way to get ready for summer.\n
