SUMMARY:Ready – Set – Camp!
DESCRIPTION:For campers entering K – 2nd grade with an adult.\nReady-Set-Camp! is a session for our youngest campers who aren’t quite ready for a full week at camp on their own to get to experience the fun and adventure of camp with a parent or guardian.\n\n\nSession:\n\n\n3B: June 2-4, 2026\n\n\n\n\nRates:\n\n\nChild: $65\n\n\nAdult: $185\n\n\n\n\n
