SUMMARY:Leaders-in-Training II
DESCRIPTION:For campers who have completed 9th-11th grade.\nLeaders at Camp (LIT II)\nThis program is designed to help older campers transition from being campers to serving as leaders in the camp community. Learn about servant leadership and build communication and relational ministry skills. LITs participate in a variety of activities that include camp “classics” (swimming, arts and crafts, and tackling the ropes course, among others), teambuilding, shadowing camp staff, overnight campouts, and more.\n\n\nSession:\n\n\n3A: June 28-July 4, 2026\n\n\n\n\nRates:\n\n\n$515 per camper\n\n\n\n\n
