SUMMARY:Leaders-in-Training I
DESCRIPTION:Leaders in the Community (LIT I)\nThis program is designed to help older campers transition from being campers to leaders within their local community. Through hands-on service projects and engaging with community organizations, LITs will develop essential servant leadership skills while enhancing their communication and relational ministry abilities.\n\n\nSession:\n\n\n1B: June 14-20, 2026\n\n\n\n\nRates:\n\n\n$515 per camper\n\n\n\n\n
